*with P. Brosnan: {{cite journal|title=Periods and Igusa Local Zeta functions|journal=Int. Math. Res. Notices|volume=49|year=2003|pages=2655–2670|url=http://imrn.oxfordjournals.org/content/2003/49/2655.short}}
