'''Otto Dersch''' (born March 17, 1848 in [[Ortenberg, Hesse]])<ref>{{citation|title=Jahrbuch des höheren Schulwesens|volume=12|publisher=B. G. Teubner|year=1891|page=136|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ar8wAQAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA136}}.</ref> was a German mathematician who worked in algebraic geometry. He was teacher and then director of a secondary school in [[Offenbach am Main]], and then became director of a secondary school in [[Darmstadt]] until at least 1915.<ref>{{citation|title=Das Fotoalbum für Weierstraß / A Photo Album for Weierstrass|first=Reinhard|last=Bölling|publisher=Springer-Verlag|year=2013|isbn=9783322802811|page=47|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WHgkBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA47}}.</ref>

